text: Convenient place to have lunch while at the Park X. We had a good break in between our Gocart activity and our ATV ride.
Superb food with handful of choices. Can be unbearably hot on summer days. Outside view is very nice.
Ate freshly made Roto Canai telur! The staff was friendly at the Eoti Canai stall, the drinks store was barely functional though. Staff not present or busy elsewhere even though no crowd.
We had breakfast here. The food was nice but i hope they can improve their service. Even its self service here but they are not systematic. I have to wait for a looong time for the roti canai.
